    Z "Por favor, entra y ve a la cocina mientras cojo mis cosas."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:31
translate spanish d6a_ec888e26:

    # Z "I will let Emilia know you're here."
    Z "Avisaré a Emilia de que estás aquí."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:32
translate spanish d6a_e3358cc8:

    # Z "She will get you some refreshments. I bet you're not yet used to the heat of the desert."
    Z "Te traerá unos refrescos. Seguro que aún no te has acostumbrado al calor del Desierto."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:35
translate spanish d6a_0f0526fb:

    # Z "I will let [W] know you're here."
    Z "Avisaré a [W] de que estás aquí."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:36
translate spanish d6a_ed61f695:

    # Z "She will take care of you. Walking under the desert sun is never easy for newcomers."
    Z "Ella cuidará de ti. Caminar bajo el sol del Desierto nunca es fácil para los recién llegados."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:43
translate spanish d6a5_9074767b:

    # "When you're ready, you and [Ka] head to the city center..."
    "Cuando estás preparado, tú y [Ka] os dirigís al centro de la ciudad..."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:46
translate spanish d6a5_2a824e29:

    # Ci "Have you heard the news?"
    Ci "¿Te has enterado de las noticias?"

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:47
translate spanish d6a5_faaf6243:

    # Ci "Queen Merneith is said to have used her dragon to execute a prisoner."
    Ci "Se dice que la Reina Merneith utilizó su dragón para ejecutar a un prisionero."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:48
translate spanish d6a5_b8c692f0:

    # Ci "Some say the dragon's fire was so bright, it caused the cursed storm!"
    Ci "Algunos dicen que el fuego del dragón era tan brillante que provocó la maldita tormenta."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:51
translate spanish d6a5_13e2ec8b:

    # C "Do you think that's true?"
    C "¿Crees que es cierto?"

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:54
