    Asaw "Tengo que contarte un secreto."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:1458
translate spanish re_d6b53_de8197dd:

    # Asaw "When you let me go, during the raid..."
    Asaw "Cuando me dejaste ir, durante la incursión..."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:1459
translate spanish re_d6b53_fbc0de42:

    # Asaw "I saw how you fucked Asha's throat after you defeated her."
    Asaw "Vi cómo le jodiste la garganta a Asha después de derrotarla."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:1460
translate spanish re_d6b53_0d63d6e9:

    # Asaw "I saw the bliss in her eyes..."
    Asaw "Vi la felicidad en sus ojos..."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:1461
translate spanish re_d6b53_b0d7adcc:

    # Asaw "...and now, I think I want to find out for myself what that was about."
    Asaw "... y ahora, creo que quiero averiguar por mí misma de qué se trataba."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:1463
translate spanish re_d6b53_de8197dd_1:

    # Asaw "When you let me go, during the raid..."
    Asaw "Cuando me dejaste ir, durante la incursión..."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:1464
translate spanish re_d6b53_8dbe1280:

    # Asaw "I'll just say you made an impression on me.."
    Asaw "Sólo diré que me impresionaste..."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:1465
translate spanish re_d6b53_2db86c58:

    # Asaw "Have a man like you teach all that raider filth what they deserve, it was exciting..."
    Asaw "Que un hombre como tú enseñe a toda esa mugre de asaltantes lo que se merecen, fue emocionante..."

# game/scripts/day6.rpy:1468
translate spanish re_d6b53_bac67a18:

    # Zw "Your skin is soft, yet you are strong..."
